extendedInfo.description: Get your Android photos printed and delivered to your door for only 99 cents (Free Shipping!)Photo Prints By Mail is the easiest way to get a beautiful, colorful, high quality 4x6 photo print delivered to your door.Do you have photos on your phone that you would love to have in a photo album, on your wall, or available to give to a friend? Photo Prints By Mail makes it easy to get 4x6 prints of your photos delivered to your door.Have you ever wished you could just get one or two printed copies of a photo? Most photo sites add huge shipping costs making it too expensive to get a print or two. With Photo Prints By Mail each photo is printed and delivered for 99 cents. NO extra fees! We keep the costs low by printing our photos on thick, high quality postcards that are sent by the US Postal Service. Our photo print quality is backed by a 100% money back guarantee. If you are unhappy with the photos for any reason we'll refund your money no questions asked.How it works (in 4 easy steps)* Open the app and choose a photo from your phones photo library* Enter your mailing address and email address (first run only)* Pay 99 cents (No shipping fees!)A beautiful, glossy, 300 dpi photo print will be delivered to your door in 3-7 days.You can also print your photos right from galleries and albums such as: QuickPic, picplz, PicsIn and pho.to.You can use Photo Prints by Mail to print from your favorite photo editor and effects apps like: PicSay, Vignette, Camera360, FxCamera, Camera Zoom FX, Retro Camera and PhotoFunia.Download the app now - it is free. See how easy it is to get a photo delivered to your door.
